ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectPlenipotentiary Conference of the International Telecommunication Union ** RATIFICATION **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the FINAL ACTS of the PLENIPOTENTIARY CONFERENCE of the INTERNATIONAL TELECOMMUNICATION UNION (Antalya, 2006) and to maintain Canada's reservations and declarations adopted at the Conference.
